title: Canberra .NET user group - October
eventShortDescription: ​Have you ever wondered how your bits and bytes travel between your PC to all the servers on the Internet? In this session, we will take a virtual road-trip out your router, through some Internet Exchange Points, under the ocean in some submarine cables and speed along some of the widest sections of the Internet Superhighway.
